{"id": 566, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪种迟到最令人厌烦？", "description": "生活辣么美妙，难道你们在来的路上都没有停下来赏个花吗？", "record_count": 3782, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194428smMcvHBLAiCpd9kO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-12T11:09:57Z", "options": [{"id": 16384, "content": "只要是迟到就很讨厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242237}, {"id": 16385, "content": "饭桌上 就等那一个迟到的人 饿啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223162}, {"id": 17921, "content": "都烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130933}, {"id": 18177, "content": "最倒霉的事是在约小三的时候迟到，正好撞见女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257932}, {"id": 16386, "content": "因个人可以避免的迟到而延误大家的行程，却没丝毫的歉意", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207748}, {"id": 16387, "content": "每次都是迟到的最后一个，没有更早，只有最迟！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233387}, {"id": 16899, "content": "吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250276}, {"id": 16388, "content": "领导姗姗来迟，却在批评后面迟到的下属。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161550Soe10GWXgdw8ifUu.jpg", "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225838}, {"id": 16391, "content": "叫你几分钟内到指定地点等他（她），结果到了很长时间仍然看不到他（她）", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244857}, {"id": 16648, "content": "我都结束了，你还没开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197716}, {"id": 18953, "content": "做爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262014}, {"id": 16394, "content": "大姨妈迟到一两个月最厌烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231574}, {"id": 16395, "content": "自己迟到了，然后还细数对方以前迟到的历史，证明自己迟到是理所当然的人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245122}, {"id": 16396, "content": "约会时本来以为自己已经迟到了，结果还是早到了半个小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170441}, {"id": 79886, "content": "是说我吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614458}, {"id": 16398, "content": "我的另一边究竟什么时候才会到？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153105}, {"id": 16399, "content": "对于大家都等一个人这件事毫无歉意，并且理由是打游戏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122150}, {"id": 18960, "content": "每次都等那人好久,结果我不小心迟到一次就hhhhhh了?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211305cFK2CgzuTyeraA9O.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262058}, {"id": 16401, "content": "经常误汽车误火车误飞机", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75588}, {"id": 16402, "content": "卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224987}, {"id": 16403, "content": "每次约好了时间，迟到了还说快到了快到了，在路上……你妹的，是从西藏过来的吗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219115}, {"id": 16404, "content": "工资迟发……", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245256}, {"id": 17428, "content": "迟到了还装作没有答应过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253373}, {"id": 16407, "content": "所有迟到都令人厌烦。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215666}, {"id": 16408, "content": "天天迟到死性不改，还怨公交怨天气怨社会", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180142}, {"id": 19482, "content": "等待是最孤独的。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265001}, {"id": 16667, "content": "跟团迟到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191513}, {"id": 17947, "content": "明明家里住的近多了，还每次约会迟到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250593}, {"id": 16412, "content": "说好7点开始Raid，结果8点多才齐人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 16415, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245375}, {"id": 16416, "content": "提醒了不要迟到还是迟到了的bb", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243928}, {"id": 16417, "content": "自己很在意是否能在約定的時間到達地點 然而 他們卻不以為然", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240639}, {"id": 16418, "content": "已经蹲在厕所上，?却迟到了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245426}, {"id": 16674, "content": "天天迟到的飘过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248475}, {"id": 16419, "content": "到点了，人没出现，还联系不上", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 18723, "content": "那种迟到都令人厌烦，不尊守时间是中国人一大通病。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240665}, {"id": 16420, "content": "外卖！\r\n说好的半小时内送达呢？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 42276, "content": "明明说好了，然后忽然告诉你变主意，接着你没回复她就当你答应了，自作主张", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429564}, {"id": 16423, "content": "为什么有些人就认为比别人迟到一点就能显示出自己的重要性？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112597}, {"id": 16935, "content": "心里认为他是故意的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147096}, {"id": 16936, "content": "或者是 自己不喜欢的人  自己不愿意等的人而让自己等他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147096}, {"id": 16426, "content": "你到哪了，我都到门口了\n我也就还有还有两三分钟\n然后俩煞笔在楼下公交站相遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223367}, {"id": 16427, "content": "位置比自己高的迟到了却毫无歉意，自己还要忍气吞声说没事。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214920}, {"id": 17451, "content": "从学生到现在工作了，都有迟到的习惯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252407}, {"id": 16428, "content": "领导秘书天天迟到。好无语啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245594}, {"id": 16430, "content": "跟男票约会不迟到 跟朋友就总会迟到", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203312}, {"id": 17712, "content": "马上要开车了，人还没影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255197}, {"id": 17457, "content": "迟到有不厌烦的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250377}, {"id": 16691, "content": "第二天他也迟到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232954}, {"id": 16440, "content": "每逢佳节必迟到，迟到还要装大爷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245795}]}